item.dc:creator: @SFate SFate
item.description:
@SFate wrote:

Just enter the IP, and if the port is 43594 leave it alone. Then enter username/password and you should be able to log on.

IP = dipsetscape.no-ip.info
Port = 43594 (Don’t have to enter, its default)

Username: Name seen on server
Password: used to log in <-- lol. Assuming you should know these anyways.
